Huge letoff for @Frenfordfc as Ryan sees his clearance charged down by Mosanya, but just like last time he fluffs the chance to seal it for Wormley.  Loose ball then fired goalwards but blocked. Deep in added time here. #ECL

Should be game over. Mosanya put through, breaks in to the @Frenfordfc box, but bizarrely opts to square to a teammate and finds a defender instead! 

Now in the Wormley box Gray gets a shot away, but it's easy for Hayward. #ECL
Mistakes from the Wormley then @Frenfordfc defences almost present chances. Inbetween, Hayward did well to claim a dangerous low ball, with Kirby lurking, inbetween those moments. #ECL

Sub James floats in a free kick which Hayward punches away. @Frenfordfc apoeal he clattered someone in the process but the officials think differently.

About five minutes left. 2-1 Wormley. #ECL

Heatley fires just over from outside the Wormley box. 

@Frenfordfc 2-1 down with less than 10 minutes to go. #ECL

Daly's free kick just inside the Wormley half almost catches Hayward out - he has to punch it out from underneath his own crossbar.

@Frenfordfc need an equaliser to stay top. #ECL

A few dangerous balls in to the box from @Frenfordfc since conceding without anyone getting on the end of them. Now then, how did Wormley not score there to go 3-1 up? Ryan somehow keeps the close range effort out to keep his side in it. #ECL

No escape this time for @Frenfordfc, who were caught napping from a quickly taken Wormley free kick. Played to Mosanya, who runs towards the box before unleashing a great strike that beats Ryan by his near post. #ECL

Off the underside of the bar! Escape for @Frenfordfc. Terrific strike 25 yards out from Evans that comes back off the upright. Rebound headed over by Beattie at the back post, but, as you can see, Wormley have now scored. #ECL
GOAL!  Wormley Rovers 2-1 @Frenfordfc.  #ECL
Some goal that would have been for @Frenfordfc as Heatley tries his luck at least 25 yards out which forces Hayward to parry it away. Daly fires wide now from outside the Wormley box. #ECL

Dangerous low ball from Hammond which I think Bartrip does well to clear. Wormley still pushing, but @Frenfordfc now with a free kick in a decent position, which Daly opts to the float to the back post rather than go for goal, but Hayward claims. 1-1. An hour gone here. #ECL

Poor defending from @Frenfordfc. Caught too narrow, with Empson running through the middle, before firing just wide from 25 yards.

At the other end, a shot well wide from distance by Gray, then Booker's cross-cum-shot tests the alertness of the Wormley keeper. #ECL

Another dangerous free kick from Wormley that's just beyond the head of Dash in the box. 

@Frenfordfc still in the dressing rooms in these opening five minutes of the 2nd half. #ECL

Scare for @Frenfordfc as Ryan is caught in two minds whether to claim a Wormley free kick. It's headed up in the air then headed on before the keeper claims. 

Now a scramble from a corner, and Ryan makes a superb save at close range to deny the hosts retaking the lead. #ECL
